title: DDFP 334: Free agency & C.J. Spiller
itunes:title: DDFP 334: Free agency & C.J. Spiller
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank to discuss where Ndamukong Suh, DeMarco Murray and others could land in free agency and possible teams for Andre Johnson. Plus, minutes BEFORE the LeSean McCoy trade, running back C.J. Spiller joins the show to discuss where he would like to end up playing next season. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
